  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1  ; \u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Increase in bus fare; People seeking rail transport",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "It was observed that train services were running as usual at Colombo Fort main railway station today.",
        "Due to the sudden increase in bus fares, more people are resorting to rail transport.",
        "At the same time, due to the shortage of diesel, it was observed that there was very little private transport in Thalai Nagar Colombo."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
